</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_168" id="84r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> zu sand Sebolt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>
            ewch <expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> frewntschaft, die ir uns von der lewfft
                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> botschaft und
            geschrift <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> beweiset, und
            <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, das umb ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu
                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. Lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, so
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns ettlich <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt fürbracht, wie daz in von
                <expan>ettlich<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Österr<ex>eich</ex></expan> reten und
            dienern und <add>in</add> seinen landen etc. ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dis</expan>. </ab>
</div>
